                                "stop": 10.95,
                                "byte_start": 28672,
                                "byte_stop": 72558,
                                "text": "The opinion in 77-1254, Vance, Secretary of State versus Bradley will be announced by Mr. Justice White."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 10.95,
                        "stop": 87.226,
                        "byte_start": 72558,
